<br>
<!--EZCODE CENTER START--><div style="text-align:center"><!--EZCODE FONT START--><span style="color:red;font-family:helvetica;font-size:medium;">HOW TO APPLY</span><!--EZCODE FONT END--></div><!--EZCODE CENTER END--><br>
<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE FONT START--><span style="font-family:comic sans ms;font-size:medium;"><!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong>If you feel you would be an asset to Odysseys,<br>
Using the guidelines below, send us your application via E-Mail to:</strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END--></span><!--EZCODE FONT END-->  <br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE FONT START--><span style="color:red;font-family:comic sans ms;font-size:large;"><!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong><!--EZCODE CENTER START--><div style="text-align:center">odysseyseq@yahoo.com</div><!--EZCODE CENTER END--></strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END--></span><!--EZCODE FONT END--><br>
<br>
Who you are. (Class, Level)<br>
Your regular playing hours<br>
How many AA's you have.<br>
Which Luclin/POP flags/keys do you have<br>
Your alts and their levels.<br>
Do you have your epic?<br>
Your raid experience - planes, dragons, etc.<br>
What is you prior guild history.<br>
Your goals in Odysseys, and what can you do for Odysseys.<br>
<br>
<br>
After an informal interview and evaluation with Dreamstalker/Minz and Odyssey's Class leader for your class, they will vote to extend a trial membership to you.  Trial membership lasts aproximately 30 days.  That will gives us and you a chance to get to know you and how well suited you are for our raid schedule.  All full members of Odysseys will then vote based on raid attendance, AA points earned during the application process and an effort to get up to date with flags and keys.  Once a full member in Odysseys  you will be on a 45 day probation.  <br>
<br>
How to get to know the people in Odysseys:<br>
<br>
<br>
1) Attend Raids <br>
2) Focusing on the task at hand during the raids<br>
3) Group with our members outside of raids<br>
4) Talk in Guild Chat (dont be so quiet that no one gets to know you)<br>
5) Help spot targets <br>
<br>
